    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392780/extras/0bde514617bdb47e6ee480b524699d5b.avif?t=1729193544\" width=615 height=70 /></span>电影般的游戏体验。扮演灵兽，踏上追寻目标和命运的征途。探索一个神奇而 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美丽的世界，让过去、现在和未来的幻象指引你的前路。收集精华并寻找人间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艺品来搭建起连接物质世界的桥梁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个单人游戏故事。这是一个充满神秘、阴谋和冒险的故事。游历七片壮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丽非凡的大地，见证一个家庭在面对眼前重重挑战时的感人故事。并肩同行，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次一小步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392780/extras/e313ac088ab79818a6721bb110b67101.avif?t=1729193544\" width=615 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次充满神秘、阴谋和发现的旅程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个关于爱和家庭，感人至深的故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >附有动听的配乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集精华</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找人间艺品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲历各种幻象</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用符文石召唤其他灵兽到你身边</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞥见浮光掠影</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392780/extras/7ff230efdf7ed33d386ac7508dad76d6.avif?t=1729193544\" width=615 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，跟着精灵穿越所有精彩的关卡，聆听美妙的配乐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括所有21支乐曲，总时长超过1小时。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常适合学习、做家务、锻炼或放松时在后台播放。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带动态定向镜头。</p></li></ul>",
